ood \\n9. Very good \\n10. Excellent\"},\"title\":{\"en\":\"National grading\"}},\"language\":{\"id\":\"http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG\",\"type\":\"Concept\",\"inScheme\":{\"id\":\"http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language\",\"type\":\"ConceptScheme\"},\"notation\":\"language\",\"prefLabel\":{\"en\":\"English\"}},\"title\":{\"en\":\"Overall Assessment\"},\"dcType\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/assessment/3484bd7e51\",\"type\":\"Concept\",\"inScheme\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/assessment/25831c2\",\"type\":\"ConceptScheme\"},\"prefLabel\":{\"en\":\"continuous evaluation\"}}},\"description\":{\"en\":\"The overall grade is influenced by, and composed of, various types of written assignments and a final paper.\"},\"title\":{\"en\":\"Overall Assessment\"}},\"specifiedBy\":{\"id\":\"urn:epass:learningAchievementSpec:3\",\"type\":\"LearningAchievementSpecification\",\"thematicArea\":[{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/isced-f/0211\",\"type\":\"Concept\",\"inScheme\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/isced-f/25831c2\",\"type\":\"ConceptScheme\"},\"prefLabel\":{\"en\":\"Audio-visual techniques and media production\"}},{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/isced-f/02\",\"type\":\"Concept\",\"inScheme\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/isced-f/25831c2\",\"type\":\"ConceptScheme\"},\"prefLabel\":{\"en\":\"Arts and humanities\"}},{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/isced-f/021\",\"type\":\"Concept\",\"inScheme\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/isced-f/25831c2\",\"type\":\"ConceptScheme\"},\"prefLabel\":{\"en\":\"Arts\"}}],\"creditPoint\":{\"id\":\"urn:epass:creditPoint:1\",\"type\":\"CreditPoint\",\"framework\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/education-credit/6fcec5c5af\",\"type\":\"Concept\",\"inScheme\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/education-credit/25831c2\",\"type\":\"ConceptScheme\"},\"prefLabel\":{\"en\":\"European Credit Transfer System\"}},\"point\":\"6.00\"},\"learningOutcome\":{\"id\":\"u