 technologies\"}},{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/dcf/99vvo91542\",\"type\":\"Concept\",\"inScheme\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/dcf/25831c2\",\"type\":\"ConceptScheme\"},\"prefLabel\":{\"en\":\"Netiquette\"}},{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/dcf/9a5d39t62b\",\"type\":\"Concept\",\"inScheme\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/dcf/25831c2\",\"type\":\"ConceptScheme\"},\"prefLabel\":{\"en\":\"Sharing through digital technologies\"}},{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/dcf/3h9eab1489\",\"type\":\"Concept\",\"inScheme\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/dcf/25831c2\",\"type\":\"ConceptScheme\"},\"prefLabel\":{\"en\":\"Evaluating data, information and digital content\"}},{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/dcf/9i6ta81748\",\"type\":\"Concept\",\"inScheme\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/dcf/25831c2\",\"type\":\"ConceptScheme\"},\"prefLabel\":{\"en\":\"Browsing, searching and filtering data, information and digital content\"}}],\"title\":{\"en\":\"Online Communities\"}},\"learningOutcomeSummary\":{\"id\":\"urn:epass:note:9\",\"type\":\"Note\",\"noteLiteral\":{\"en\":\"The qualification holder is able to:\\n(1) understand the logics of datafication and the ideologies of sharing through digital media; \\n(2) critically assess online sharing practices with a specific focus on ethical issues emerging from these new practices.\"}},\"learningSetting\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/learning-setting/6fd4685715\",\"type\":\"Concept\",\"inScheme\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/learning-setting/25831c2\",\"type\":\"ConceptScheme\"},\"prefLabel\":{\"en\":\"formal learning\"}},\"mode\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/learning-assessment/9191af2ed9\",\"type\":\"Concept\",\"inScheme\":{\"id\":\"http://data.europa.eu/snb/learning-assessment/25831c2\",\"type\":\"ConceptScheme\"},\"prefLabel\":{\"en\":\"Presential\"}},\"language\":{\"id\":\"http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG\",\"type\":\"Concept\",\"inScheme\":{\"id\":\"htt